http://hl7.org/fhir/imagingselection-status5.0.0  availableAvailableThe selected resources are available..
http://hl7.org/fhir/imagingselection-status5.0.0  entered-in-errorEntered in ErrorThe imaging selection has been withdrawn following a release. This electronic record should never have existed, though it is possible that real-world decisions were based on it. (If real-world activity has occurred, the status should be "cancelled" rather than "entered-in-error".).
